  "acceptance_criteria": "Can favourite/unfavourite and remote server sees the Like activity; can boost and remote server sees Announce; home timeline shows posts from followed accounts in correct order; thread context returns ancestors oldest-first and descendants oldest-first; follow request flow works for locked accounts",
